results.title: Live, Laugh, Lobotomy, Cross Stitch Pattern; Snarky, Dark-Humor Digital Pattern
results.description:
Live, Laugh, Lobotomy, Cross Stitch Pattern; Snarky, Dark-Humor Digital Pattern

We've all seen the "Live, Laugh, Love" signs, but that might feel a little too sunshiny for some of us. This dark humor pattern acknowledges that sometimes the darker side of life can't just be smiled away. 

Lobotomies themselves have a horrific history and while some forms of the procedure still exist today (though not performed with an icepick!), it was once used to silence a wide swath of people who were labeled "different" by society. I don't want to make light of that barbarous history with this pattern, but to provide an outlet for the complicated feelings surrounding it. Mental health is a human right. 

A Blackwork version of this pattern is also available in my shop.

* This is a PDF pattern for you to stitch*

Finished pattern is 115 stitches wide by 128 stitches high.

Total size depends on the Aida cloth size:
    	 18ct— 6.4 x 7.1 inches (or 16.2 x 18.1 cm)
    	 16ct— 7.2 x 8 inches (or 18.3 x 120.3 cm)
     	 14ct— 8.2 x 9.1 inches (or 20.9 x 23.2 cm)

PDF includes:
		• Preview sheet with sizing info
		• Single-page symbols on color block sheet
		• Enlarged symbols on color block sheets
		• Enlarged black & white symbols sheets
		• Thread color key (DMC colors)

❤  SIZING:  
SIZE CHARTS can be found in the product photos- please take your measurements and carefully review to choose your size as everyone’s “true to size” and every shirt brand runs differently.  You will also find the flat measurements for our products for your convenience so you can measure your favorite fitting shirt to also choose your size if you prefer.  

We have the chest measurement, length measurement, sleeve length as well as the flat width measurements for all of our available shirt options.  Our ladies shirts are FITTED, so if you are in between sizes or prefer a looser fit, please size up.  If you prefer a longer shirt for leggings or if you are tall we recommend going with the unisex crew neck shirt vs. the fitted ladies.  We do provide lengths of each so you can choose the best option for you.      

If you are having trouble viewing the sizing chart measurements we do have larger size charts available upon request.  

❤  PLUS SIZES:  
Our PLUS SIZES are NOT comparable to other plus size stores.  We do not have 0X or 1x, our shirts go from XL to 2XL.  This means our plus sizes run smaller if you use that size model.   That is why we stress measuring vs. choosing your size you usually wear.   If in between sizes we recommend sizing up.   We also carry unisex sizing if you prefer that fit over ladies.  Those tend to be roomier and longer if that is what you are looking for.  

***We don’t accept returns or exchanges for sizing issues due to the fact that our products are custom made special for you, so we want you to be able to choose the perfect size for you the first time around.  We are here to help if you have sizing questions.  If an error is made on our part we will quickly take care of it for you.  Please contact us within 5 business days of receiving your item.***

❤  SUBSTRATE OPTIONS:  (options available are stated in each individual listing)
 
HOLOGRAPHIC SPANGLE BLING: 
Spangle is NOT a rhinestone, it is a flat, hole less super blingy holographic dot.  Most people are not familiar with the term “Spangle” yet, as it is still an up and coming fashion trend. It is lightweight and won’t fade or lose it’s luster.  The colors are vibrant and have an amazing Holographic sparkling bling that is sure to be noticed. Since it is flat, it won’t irritate your arms or fall off if you catch it on something. Spangle is a more cost effective than rhinestones, but has the same bling factor.  You can comfortably wear your amazing new shirt while you workout, sleep, or during the day just for fun.  
  
FULL COLOR PRINTED MATTE VINYL:  
This isn’t your cheap vinyl that you get at your local hobby store.  This is quality commercial grade super thin vinyl that stretches with your garment and won’t crack, fade or peel off.  It has a thin, soft hand similar to a screen print.  It is a great substrate to use for smaller matte orders that are too small for screen printing.  Large, solid designs do seem to have a thicker feel to them, but most designs don’t have solid large pieces to them.  
 
FULL COLOR PRINTED GLITTER VINYL:
This method is good for designs that have a lot of different colors or ombre and gradient type shading.  Unprinted white areas are similar to white rainbow glitter vinyl.  Printed sections will have a shimmer effect, but are not as blingy as standard glitter vinyl.  The thickness of the full color printed glitter vinyl is on the thicker side similar to standard glitter vinyl.  

❤ TRANSFER ONLY OPTION (no shirt will be provided)- 
With all the crafty people out there a lot of people prefer to DIY when it comes to blinging out their items.  For this reason we offer the transfer only option.   You can apply our transfers with a professional heat press (our recommended application method) or with a household iron.  We include instructions for both applications as well as links to videos showing each method if you prefer to see the application vs. reading instructions.  

 
❤  SHIPPING: 
 For our already made designs, we typically ship within 1-2 business days  (M-F) if you are ordering one of our standard line of black shirts.  We stock black shirts and hoodie sweatshirts in all sizes so we can quickly ship your order.  Another reason is bling “pops” best and really stands out on black.   If another color shirt is selected or requested, then shipping time will be slightly longer depending on our ordering rotation.  

Custom special order designs are usually completed and proof sent to you within a week and shipped out shortly after approval.  

We ship all of our packages insured and with tracking.  This gives our customers a piece of mind to know that their custom bling shirts will safely arrive and their purchase is covered if the postal service was to lose, damage or deliver your package to the wrong address.  Such situations are rare, but if you happen to run into an issue please reach out to us and we can help guide you through the claims process.

In order to make a claim with the postal service if your item happens to show up damaged in any way you will need to keep your packaging.  Please don’t throw it away until you have closely inspected your item and it is damage free.  They will also require photos of the damage.  

We try to keep shipping costs as low as possible for our customers and items may often be tightly packed, so please be careful when opening your items to avoid accidental damage from sharp objects.

Please use the color names as in the color charts when requesting custom colors vs. “light blue” since we have 3 different shades of light blue.  Colors are approximate and with variations in monitor colors it may slightly differ depending on your screen settings.  If you have color questions please contact us prior to purchasing.

For exact color representation please refer to our color charts in the product photos.  The computer generated bling “sparkles” in the mock ups are not part of the design and are only there to show you that the design is bling.
